plot: Delinquent girl boss meets and conflicts with an orphan girl who lives an isolated life after the dramatic deaths of her parents. She plays the piano, but stands up against her lecherous guardian, who is also a school official.
title: Kyôfu joshikôkô: Onna bôryoku kyôshitsu
